Allows adding notes to a specific commit. 

Create a new note
```bash
git notes add -m "Comment"
git notes add -m "Comment" <commit_hash>
```

Edit an existing note
```bash
git notes edit -m "Comment"
git notes edit -m "Comment" <commit_hash>
```

Remove a note
```bash
git notes remove
git notes remove <commit_hash>
```

Notes can be organized in a namespace
```bash
git notes add -m "Comment" --ref=<namespace>
```

## Related commands

* Notes are shown using [[git log]].
* Notes are pushed to the remote using [[git push]].
* Notes are pulled using [[git fetch]].
